'''Picking the Bones''' is the sixteenth [[mission]] in Episode 2, [[Never Forgive, Never Forget]]. It takes place at [[Amleth Prime]] in the [[Amleth]] system.

Epic is currently bugged, and only requires a skill check of 136.

